<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّاءٍ مَّهِينٍ}</span> ... ضَعِيفٍ حَقِيرٍ؛ وَهُوَ النُّطْفَةُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَرَارٍ مَّكِينٍ}</span> ... مَكَانٍ حَصِينٍ مُتَمَكِّنٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَدَرٍ}</span> ... وَقْتٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كِفَاتًا}</span> ... وِعَاءً تَضُمُّ الأَحْيَاءَ وَالأَمْوَاتَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَوَاسِيَ شَامِخَاتٍ}</span> ... جِبَالًا ثَوَابِتَ، مُرْتَفِعَاتٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُرَاتًا}</span> ... عَذْبًا، سَائِغًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظِلٍّ}</span> ... هُوَ دُخَانُ جَهَنَّمَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِي ثَلَاثِ شُعَبٍ}</span> ... يَتَفَرَّعُ مِنْهُ ثَلَاثُ قِطَعٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا ظَلِيلٍ}</span> ... لَا يُظِلُّ مِنْ حَرِّ ذَلِكَ اليَوْمِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يُغْنِي}</span> ... لَا يَدْفَعُ، وَلَا يَقِي.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِشَرَرٍ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> الشَّرَارَةُ:</span> مَا يَتَطَايَرُ مِنَ النَّارِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالْقَصْرِ}</span> ... كَالبِنَاءِ المُشَيَّدِ فِي العِظَمِ وَالاِرْتِفَاعِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جِمَالَتٌ صُفْرٌ}</span> ... كَأَنَّ الشَّرَرَ إِبِلٌ سُودٌ يَمِيلُ لَوْنُهَا إِلَى الصُّفْرَةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَيْدٌ}</span> ... حِيلَةٌ فِي الخَلَاصِ مِنَ العَذَابِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٤١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظِلَالٍ}</span> ... ظِلِّ الأَشْجَارِ الوَارِفَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَنِيئًا}</span> ... مُتَهَنِّئِينَ مِنْ غَيْرِ تَنْغِيصٍ، وَلَا كَدَرٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَدِيثٍ بَعْدَهُ}</span> ... كِتَابٍ وَكَلَامٍ بَعْدَ القُرْآنِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>